    "The outputs of Llama 2 70B demonstrate mixed results.",
    "At the quantitative level, the model displays a degree of misalignment with the reference text in terms of semantic and thematic similarity while evidencing good alignment on structural and sentimental fronts.",
    "Where the model excels in this narrative task is through interpretive originality.",
    "Llama 2, alone among our tested models, demonstrates a willingness to consider the deeper questions of the reference text and address them with a readiness to avoid easy, satisfying resolution.",
